==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Redroot
<hw>Red"root`</hw> <pr>(r?d"r?t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name of several plants having red roots, as the New Jersey tea
(see under <er>Tea</er>), the gromwell, the bloodroot, and the
<xex>Lachnanthes tinctoria</xex>, an endogenous plant found in sandy
swamps from Rhode Island to Florida.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Redsear</ent>⟦br⟧
